I know these are always a bit wanky but I’ve lost about 7kg since January this year and feel I’m at a really good place at the moment. Fitness is a constant journey, it’s never easy but it’s so genuinely rewarding. Not just aesthetically but mentally, I’ve said time and time again how much it can positively impact you... as long as you don’t let it rule your life. BALANCE is key!
